text: hello <@U19MP2N67>.  I’m sure there are many ways to solve the problem, but I have had decent luck using delve (<https://github.com/derekparker/delve>) and wrote a wiki entry for it here <https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric/wiki/Go-Development-Portal#delve>
This is GDB command-line style debugging though…if IDE breakpoints, etc, are you thing, YMMV
feel free to update the wiki with more details if you find something else that works well
